---

<Base title="CV — Mads Rudolph" description="CV of Mads Rudolph — Elektroteknologi (B.Eng.) student at DTU. PCB design, embedded firmware, and electronics debugging.">
  <div class="page-head">
    <span class="label">CV</span>
    <h1>Curriculum vitae</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      The short version is below. The <a href="/projects">project writeups</a> are the long
      version — the evidence behind every skill listed here. For a formatted PDF or references,
      <a href="mailto:mads28122001@hotmail.dk">get in touch</a>.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2>Profile</h2>
  <p>
    Electrical Engineering student at DTU with a strong focus on electronics and embedded systems.
    I design and fabricate PCBs in KiCad, write firmware for microcontroller-based hardware, and
    debug at the bench — from a single footprint to a fully working device. Curious and self-driven;
    I build the tool when the right one doesn't exist. Seeking an engineering internship (praktik)
    from January 2027 and a student job alongside my studies.
  </p>

  <h2>Skills</h2>
  {
    skillGroups.map((group) => (
      <p>
        <span class="label">{group.label}</span><br />
        {group.items.join(' · ')}
      </p>
    ))
  }

  <h2>Education</h2>
  {
    education.map((item) => (
      <div style="margin-bottom: 1.1rem;">
        <span class="label">{item.period}</span>
        <div><strong>{item.title}</strong></div>
        <div style="color: var(--ink-soft);">{item.org}</div>
        {item.notes && <div style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.92rem;">{item.notes}</div>}
      </div>
    ))
  }

  <h2>Employment history</h2>
  <p style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.92rem; margin-top: -0.25rem;">
    Service and seasonal work through my studies — flexible enough to keep engineering first, and
    each one taught me to stay organised and communicate under pressure.
  </p>
  {
    experience.map((item) => (
      <div style="margin-bottom: 1.1rem;">
        <span class="label">{item.period}</span>
        <div>
          <strong>{item.role}</strong>, {item.org} — {item.place}
        </div>
        {item.notes && <div style="color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 0.92rem;">{item.notes}</div>}
      </div>
    ))
  }

  <h2>Languages & interests</h2>
  <p>
    Danish (native), English (fluent). Outside engineering: hi-fi and vinyl, CAD modelling,
    FPV drone racing, and cooking.
  </p>

  <hr />
  <p>
    <span class="label">Contact</span><br />
    <a href="mailto:mads28122001@hotmail.dk">mads28122001@hotmail.dk</a> ·
    <a href="https://github.com/MadsRudolph">github.com/MadsRudolph</a> · Kongens Lyngby, Denmark
    <!-- VERIFY: phone (+45 20 65 27 14) and street address are intentionally kept off the public page; they're on the PDF you send directly. Say the word to add them. -->
  </p>
</Base>
